{"tid":921033,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解人會選擇去信教","createTime":"2018-11-29T09:04:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T03:46:17.000Z","uid":195975,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b4edce4cad3d5cea03f157b2fcf1f8cd1dbcacdb","tid":921033,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:04:52.000Z","msg":"想知從心理學角度係點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"087ca7a5fa6add032a88fd9e3d6c41fa0161c092","tid":921033,"uid":204624,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:05:14.000Z","msg":"你理得人啫"},{"pid":"f9f74f48f6e23f9438bb13eb02c58f6aca06cf6a","tid":921033,"uid":2757,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:05:24.000Z","msg":"溝女"},{"pid":"8db7472362a2d2d8847a989289b76fc45e8b2e1b","tid":921033,"uid":82450,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:18:18.000Z","msg":"如果你不接受耶蘇，你這一生都是沒有意義的，不論你的成就有多少。只有接受祂，你就是快樂的、滿足的。屋企個家族過半都係耶撚，我焗住扮信教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c95268c4002154f3b03ecf9430a9a7dc8540d481","tid":921033,"uid":140092,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:32:56.000Z","msg":"宗教係信仰，科學係信仰，無神論係信仰，乜鳩都係信仰。<br />\n<br />\n「教」只係將信仰具體化嘅方式only。<br />\n<br />\n而點解要具體化係因為人想聚集有共同理念嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n點解想聚集係因為人嘅天性。"},{"pid":"d6b2a80aaa2a44743173fd9c545d41f1193bd0c6","tid":921033,"uid":67225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T11:15:26.000Z","msg":"埋堆/取暖"},{"pid":"2cf4dbf992c0b6ca9e6990af8d09a05848015403","tid":921033,"uid":196420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T11:16:32.000Z","msg":"自己一個人頂唔住<br />\n想搵野/人同佢分擔"},{"pid":"483474f1ab65d2a1a324c7f598ffdfe53356f195","tid":921033,"uid":186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T11:16:33.000Z","msg":"入學加分"},{"pid":"bb27eff613f5576dfdbbb8ab722ae0c7017b836c","tid":921033,"uid":38738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T11:17:18.000Z","msg":"屌教友"},{"pid":"514cb65791682105d9bce0450f9cb593a5de20a2","tid":921033,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"483474f1ab65d2a1a324c7f598ffdfe53356f195","tid":921033,"uid":186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T11:16:33.000Z","msg":"入學加分"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T11:26:47.000Z","msg":"true"},{"pid":"f691d4b8385b6353602f6d7084aad6750eb58de3","tid":921033,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T12:16:18.000Z","msg":"利用教徒嘅既有印象去解釋一啲自己唔想解釋嘅行為"},{"pid":"f5625eb03133b483254c7389b0d46429dce5ff0f","tid":921033,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T12:21:01.000Z","msg":"因為神愛世人 甚至將衪的獨生兒女獻給他們"},{"pid":"717babc785198fb9222ca1b086650b93055162e4","tid":921033,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T15:15:31.000Z","msg":"錢多得濟"},{"pid":"0802662b15a9e2901de58e49af8d6d75d9de0119","tid":921033,"uid":119409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T01:14:27.000Z","msg":"生物學上分析啦<br />\n人同猩猩馬嬲係同一種群體模式<br />\n你留意，猩猩都有猩猩皇<br />\n馬嬲都一樣  所以其實人都係潛意識上會對一個君主嘅信念<br />\n由於人類開始慢慢追求真理<br />\n追求平等，所以即使我地有總統又好，皇帝又好<br />\n人類都知道其實佢地都只係一個人<br />\n所以會相信一D冇法證實佢係假嘅野<br />\n去安慰自己有一個無所不能嘅領袖係到保護緊自己<br />\n消除果種人類先天對領袖追求嘅天性"},{"pid":"da30e05c9941356b9a2050bb72a5e55e1ce87c16","tid":921033,"uid":209120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T03:04:24.000Z","msg":"其實有冇scientific method可以研究宗教入面嘅超自然現象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f9b9c078b6a5b931bcf8c884ed7f8ba293ee41","tid":921033,"uid":121701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T03:46:17.000Z","msg":"覺得人太渺小"}]}